{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":3,"day":29}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"战士歌颂红太阳","authors":["汉族战士薛锡祥"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟随毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光照，银光照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日出山光万道；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席像片墙上挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席对咱微微笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出勤前，毛主席语录记几条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下岗后，用毛主席的话做对照；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了缺点定克服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了成绩莫骄傲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士驻守在深山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天涯海角能看到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲的烈火四海的云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作红旗满天飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和咱心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱每天向毛主席作汇报；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟随毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命到底不动摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉族战士 薛锡祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的命令到草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的命令到草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水更绿呀天更蓝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命，促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设祖国的好江山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最好的马头琴拉一曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把毛主席的号召传遍大草原；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷香的鲜奶倒一碗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福毛主席万寿无疆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古族战士 扎木苏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向领袖表决心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗族战士 陶正芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边疆的茶花格外红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边疆的山水格外青；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻开《毛泽东著作选读》本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字句句照我心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教我接好革命班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“完全”“彻底”为人民；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教我紧握手中枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻警惕有敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花向着太阳转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱毛主席亲又亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大领袖一席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士字字记在心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹起芦笙唱起歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向领袖表决心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪杆笔杆握得紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把牛鬼蛇神全扫尽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花开放面朝东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火塘添柴屋里暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桂花开放遍地香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想照瑶山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山岭岭鲜花放！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向阳坡上香草长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沃土地上茶枫壮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命掀高潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑶家人变地换装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花开放面朝东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千支颂歌齐欢唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士觉悟大提高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里浪里不摇晃！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑶族战士 罗炳良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士想念毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗净我的脸的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是雅鲁藏布江；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨硬我的脚板的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是入云的雪山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保护我长大的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是毛主席派来的解放军；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我生命的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是红彤彤的宝书四卷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在我是一名战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国守卫边防线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民给我的枪拿在手上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的教导记在心坎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的书使我看清世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云雾再多也遮不住双眼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的话使我脚跟站稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山风再大也不会走偏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永世不忘的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿为保卫祖国奋勇作战；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永世不忘的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士日夜把您想念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏族战士 扎 布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（本栏由《解放军文艺》供稿）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}